songs.title: Left Foot, Right Foot (#HandsUpAnthem)
songs.lyrics:
(217 on da track)

[Hook]
Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot
Go on, hit it on 'em
Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot
Put yo hands up
Hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em
Go on, hit it on 'em
Hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em
Put yo hands up

[Verse 1]
Okay, people lets get started
I'm the turn up king
So I'm [? pipin up]
If you can't dance, baby that is ok
Left foot, right foot, come and swing my way
[?Memphis my state], but I'm always in the A
And when I do my dance, everybody's like ayy
Swag surfin' caught a wave and I ain't coming back down
Left foot, right foot, turn up right now

[Hook]
Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot
Go on, hit it on 'em
Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot
Put your hands up
Hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em
Go on, hit it on 'em
Hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em

[Verse 2]
Put your hands up, then swing
I done walked in with 217 (217 on da track man)
Left foot, right foot, then I juju on the beat
Stop reverse, okay that's a major key
Turn up right now
I just bought a whip
She wanna skedaddle, so I took her on a trip
And dabbing is a habit, I hit the quan and dip
Every time I come around, left foot, right foot

[Pre-Hook]
Turn up right now

[Hook]
Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot
Go on, hit it on 'em
Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot
Put your hands up
Hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em
Go on, hit it on 'em
Hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em
Put your hands up

[Verse 3]
Row, row, row your boat, then I hit the lean
Reverse drop, don't stop vibing to the beat
Swinging left, to the right, left, to the right
Swinging left, to the right, left, to the right
Screaming [?do 'thing he like, do 'thing he like, do 'thing he like, do 'thing he like]
Swinging left, to the right, left, to the right
Swinging left, to the right, left

[Pre-Hook]
Turn up right now

[Hook]
Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot
Go on, hit it on 'em
Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot
Put your hands up
Hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em
Go on, hit it on 'em
Hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em
Put your hands up

[Verse 4]
When I'm in the north, they turning up of course
So if you from the north you better (put your hands up)
And when I'm in the east, they turn up in the streets
So if you from the east you better (put your hands up)
And when I'm in the west, all they do is flex
So if you in the west you need to (put your hands up)
And shoutout to the south, cos I come from the south
Memphis 1020 Atlanta

[Pre Hook]
Turn up right now

[Hook]
Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot
Go on, hit it on 'em
Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot
Put your hands up
Hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em
Go on, hit it on 'em
Hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em, hit it on 'em
Put your hands up
